item.title: CVE-2022-3994|2024-08-03T01:27:53.743Z -- unknown -- authenticator
item.description: The Authenticator WordPress plugin before 1.3.1 does not prevent subscribers from updating a site's feed access token, which may deny other users access to the functionality in certain configurations.
